title: Completeness
text: Refers to whether all the data necessary is there and there is no data missing.

title: Uniqueness
text: Uniqueness refers to whether or not each value shows up just once.

title: Consistency
text: Consistency ensures data values are consistent across different systems and data sets, as well as throughout the data science process.

title: Validity
text: Validity is the property where the data makes sense in the context of the situation and the data that is being collected.
